page.title: 02MONTACUTE
page.content: {Golf Supreme { }Golf Supreme Glove Manufactures is a privately owned business owned by Mr M.Hockey. It is situated in Townsend and is a small village industry making all kinds of gloves. Golf Supreme employs six people including two directors and a number of part time workers. {Montacute Antiques} Montacute Antiques is an Antique shop which is owned privately. It is situated in South Street and the shop sells various antiques. {Milk House Restaurant} The Milk House Restaurant is a privately owned restaurant owned by Mr.& Mrs. Stead. It is situated in South Street and serves a variety of lunches and evening meals. {MORE>}
